title: Ep 1967 - Popatlal Ka Rashi Bhavishya
shortDesc: Bhide gets lot of appreciation for conducting the Society work smoothly. Jethalal and Champaklal too appreciates Bhide’s efforts towards Gokuldham Society. In the meantime, Bhide realizes that Popatlal has not signed on his cheque.

title: Ep 1968 - Popatlals new love story
shortDesc: The auto rickshaw in which Popatlal going to office breaksdown midway.Popatlal tries to look for another auto but is unable to get one. Out of desperation, Popatlal tries to take a lift and in the hurry comes in the way of a girl on a cycle

title: Ep 1969 - That girl on a bicycle
shortDesc: Popat Lal tells all his friends about the girl on the bicycle and that he thinks that she is the one who will become his life partner. But, he does not even know the girl’s name or a number. While all the society members are happy for Popal Lal,

title: Ep 1970 - Popatlal Ke Khawaab
shortDesc: Popatlal meets his love of life on a rainy day under the umbrellas. He thinks, that she is the right girl with whom he would like to spend his life with. He proposes her and she accepts his love on the second day of their meeting!

title: Ep 1971 - Popatlal Waits for Miss Tring Tring
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Popatlal seeking blessing from Champaklal before leaving to meet his love of life. He is waiting at the same place where he had met her the previous day.

title: Ep 1972 - Sodhi Ka Bhide Par Gussa
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Popatlal selling Sing Chana at VP road crossing. He is surrounded with school kids who are purchasing Sing Chana at the road crossing.

title: Ep 1973 - Search for Miss Tring Tring
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with the residents of Gokuldham Society feeling pity for Popatlal. Everyone is trying to help Popatlal at a time of financial crisis.

title: Ep 1974 - Mission Tring Tring
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Popatlal and Tapu Sena following the advice of Daya and others to begin their search for Miss Tring-Tring. Now, it is the only mission of the residents of the Gokuldham Society

title: Ep 1975 - Mission Tring Tring
shortDesc: Jethalal is instructing Bagha and Nattu Kaka to search for Miss Tring Tring on the streets around Gada Electronics. He provides the details of Miss Tring Tring’s bicycle and asked them to be alert.

title: Ep 1976 - Miss Tring Tring disappears
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal informing Daya that Popatlal is very happy after meeting his Miss Tring Tring. He further says that both are spending a good time in a coffee shop.

title: Ep 1977 - Popatlal is arrested
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Popatlal searching for Miss Tring Tring in the nearby areas of Powder Gally. Popatlal is waiting patiently at the traffic signal to meet his love of life but again he gets himself in a trouble

title: Ep 1978 - Popatlal saves Miss Tring Tring
shortDesc: Popatlal is completely gone mad for Miss Tring Tring and he wants to meet her at any cost. His wait to meet his love of life continues, as he is still standing aimlessly at the VP Road crossing for her.

title: Ep 1979 - Popatlal And Miss Tring Tring Get Into Trouble
shortDesc: In order to save their life form the goons, Popatlal and Miss Tring Tring keeps running and hiding here and there to ultimately get rescued from the trouble.On the other hand, the residents of Gokuldham society.

title: Ep 1980 - Popat Lal turns the tide.
shortDesc: The gangster points a gun at Popat Laal and is about to shoot him, but Popat Laal requests the gangster to listen to him first. He tries to explain to the gangster not to kill him, but in vain. Popat Laal also requests the gangster to let Kiran go.

title: Ep 1981 - Popatlals exclusive Interview with Irrfan Khan
shortDesc: The residents of Gokuldham Society is congratulating Popatlal for his brave act, which has helped the police in nabbing the drugs mafias. To honor the courageous journalist, Indian TV producer
